WEBVTT

00:08:28.353 --> 00:08:30.988
because my hands are always
freezing and he's so warm,

00:08:31.012 --> 00:08:34.424
where I would take my ice-cold hands
and shove them up his shirt ...

00:08:34.886 --> 00:08:36.895
press them against his hot bod.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.982
(Laughter)

00:08:39.405 --> 00:08:41.920
And he hated it so much,

00:08:41.944 --> 00:08:42.965
(Laughter)

00:08:42.989 --> 00:08:44.347
but he loved me,

00:08:44.371 --> 00:08:49.228
and after he died,
I laid in bed with Aaron

00:08:49.252 --> 00:08:51.656
and I put my hands underneath him

00:08:53.355 --> 00:08:55.845
and I felt his warmth.

00:08:58.374 --> 00:09:01.881
And I can't even tell you
if my hands were cold,